	<h1>About Note Taker</h1>

	<p>Welcome to the Note Taker project! This web application provides
		you with a simple and convenient way to manage your notes online.</p>

	<h2>Features</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Create and Save Notes: Easily jot down your thoughts, ideas,
			and reminders.</li>
		<li>Edit and Update Notes: Make changes to your notes as needed.</li>
		<li>View All Notes: Access your entire collection of notes in one
			place.</li>
		<li>Delete Notes: Delete those notes which are not useful anymore
			to you.</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>How It Works</h2>
	<p>The Note Taker application is built using JavaServer Pages (JSP)
		and Servlets. It allows you to:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Add a new note by entering text in the provided textarea and
			clicking the "Save Note" button.</li>
		<li>Edit and update existing notes by making changes to the
			textarea and clicking the "Save Note" button.</li>
		<li>View all your notes listed on the page.</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Future Enhancements</h2>
	<p>We're continuously working to improve the Note Taker
		application. Some features we're planning to add include:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Note Categories: Organize your notes into categories for
			better management.</li>
		<li>User Accounts: Create an account to save and access your
			notes securely.</li>
		<li>Sharing: Share notes with others via email or social media.</li>
	</ul>

